rows.label: tlk42350143_06_msg0001
rows.name:
At the very end, the opal coral
accessories that Kurolo made
are selling like crazy, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Orders are flooding in from people buying them
as charms for safety, or people who want to
wear something beautiful before they die, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Whatever the reason, Kurolo has contributed
to the city, mo. With this, I have
fulfilled my duty as a merchant, mo.

rows.label: tlk42350143_06_msg0004
rows.name: あとは時の流れに身を任せるも もし無事だったら また会おうも
